665
00:35:43,921 --> 00:35:44,961
No need to thank me.

666
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:46,481
I'll save anyone.

667
00:35:46,921 --> 00:35:48,441
Otherwise, I'll have to deal
with the consequences.

668
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,040
How long have you been in Africa?

669
00:35:51,401 --> 00:35:52,401
Two years.

670
00:35:52,881 --> 00:35:54,080
I applied

671
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,641
for multiple short-term missions.

672
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:56,760
Four missions in five years.

673
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:57,721
And I stay for six months each time.

674
00:35:58,441 --> 00:35:59,721
Because of your mother?

675
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,280
Yes.

676
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,121
Because my mom is here.

677
00:36:07,520 --> 00:36:08,241
What about you?

678
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,441
How have you been?

679
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:13,681
I went to Xinzhou for my Master degree.

680
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,961
Xinzhou?

681
