Why not Jiangzhou?

682
00:36:18,881 --> 00:36:20,840
Was it to avoid me?

683
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,161
Of course, not.

684
00:36:22,681 --> 00:36:23,921
Why should I avoid you?

685
00:36:25,641 --> 00:36:27,280
Where do you work now?

686
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:29,080
West District Hospital.

687
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:30,721
West District Hospital?

688
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:33,520
I'm close to your President Wang.

689
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:34,520
Which department are you in?

690
00:36:34,681 --> 00:36:35,481
Neurosurgery.

691
00:36:35,721 --> 00:36:36,641
Neurosurgery?

692
00:36:37,241 --> 00:36:39,121
We're colleagues then.

693
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:40,760
Why did you pick neurosurgery?

694
00:36:41,641 --> 00:36:43,481
Why can't I?

695
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,121
You have changed.

696
00:36:47,241 --> 00:36:48,560
You're rude now.

697
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,320
Back then,
you wouldn't even touch a frog.

698
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:52,000
Now, you break open people's skulls.

699
00:36:52,961 --> 00:36:53,961
It's been six years.

700
00:36:53,961 --> 00:36:56,320
We all change.

701
00:36:57,201 --> 00:36:58,401
You have changed too.

